{"tid":193411,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"原來用嚟solve equations嘅software統稱叫......","createTime":"2017-04-09T09:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T16:16:49.000Z","uid":33883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd175ce00a72193d993c3f096aabc8fd64d13be","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"Computer Algebra System (CAS)!<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_computer_algebra_systems\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_computer_algebra_systems&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b4e61e6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_computer_algebra_systems</a><br />\ne.g. MATLAB, Mathematica, Maxima, SageMath, SymPy, etc.<br />\n<br />\n我今日先知(如果一早知有啲咁正嘅嘢存在, 我中小學時Maths一定高分到爆晒燈, 唉)! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>SymPy</strong>(in Python)</span> solve equations好似比較麻煩同唔夠直觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 用<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>Maxima</strong></span>就就手啲同直觀啲, 正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !<br />\n<br />\n<strong>SymPy(in Python)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/09/173118_36c94ace73ca1862c2d2e953205d785a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2F173118_36c94ace73ca1862c2d2e953205d785a.jpg&h=adfa5fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Maxima</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/09/173201_91bddf492c0c9a8921c64844868ffde8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2F173201_91bddf492c0c9a8921c64844868ffde8.jpg&h=681f9adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇用開邊隻CAS呢?"},{"pid":"1d6a0c811d4e861d072490a304db1a611ebc7bee","tid":193411,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"Wolfram Alpha<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540a2452ec61da7331b2cfb3e1d3f5c2acac9d2b","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Wolfram Alpha<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔用新嘅Wolfram Mathematica, 要用隻舊嘅Wolfram Alpha嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72771d6d448e8b721a52e71056a7f516292f1231","tid":193411,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d60c0744c2a73900c655d0fbf90930952e70aac","tid":193411,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ae3e6ddcf77e9c841cf31f761dbf3e52cfa5de8","tid":193411,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"maxima"},{"pid":"70b493cf0c743a64ea15f5a0d951288283c6a098","tid":193411,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"你小學個陣有python 啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無咩幾何用<br />\n用都係Wolfram Alpha<br />\n<br />\n如果truth table 就用自己寫個個<br />\n因為幾年前睇Wolfram Alpha 個truth table<br />\n唔知多過幾多個variable就有bug<br />\n咁就自己寫左個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4913548ee242cf3740d041c3b2655b8a8bd5ad32","tid":193411,"uid":20840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"想當年中學d微積分同algebra 全部用wolfram alpha做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e613e141bffed07b347f4c89a1d27094cbcab51","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Wolfram Alpha<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔用新嘅Wolfram Mathematica, 要用隻舊嘅Wolfram Alpha嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndiu lei.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmathematica is older</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係有最新更新喎, Mathematica(2017), Alpha(2013), he he! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4e89dc014e745857a078449bd22979b9ee979e","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想當年中學d微積分同algebra 全部用wolfram alpha做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁同畀錢請槍有乜分別?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ece971cff47d6325356e399c1fbb51acd1f229","tid":193411,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:20:00.000Z","msg":"symbolab <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece80cc92dbd6b67de084df4719efd57369a6d99","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>maxima</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOpen source CAS嚟講, Maxima真係ichiban好用, 仲可以打句to_lisp()就可以轉成Common Lisp用, 好方便啫! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bf5001a149c11b462134f591d6421fb3aaa639","tid":193411,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想當年中學d微積分同algebra 全部用wolfram alpha做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁同畀錢請槍有乜分別?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分別在wolfram alpha唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf2c25894a7856788c3b415b715f1f7bc12586a","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>symbolab <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩, 呢隻仲離普, 唔駛裝, 唔駛打command, 就咁隊條equation落去就同你solve, 仲要show到step-by-step solution + real-time plot graph! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f626d26c6679d1281583a36bfa662143e25c52f6","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想當年中學d微積分同algebra 全部用wolfram alpha做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁同畀錢請槍有乜分別?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分別在wolfram alpha唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎, regular version free架喎, 係pro version先要錢!<br />\nAnyway, 你咁L醒嘅, 咁當年你Maths(尤其Pure Maths)功課咪鑊鑊滿分?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86271de59882d3b77c460a4cef5502492e4b331f","tid":193411,"uid":20840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想當年中學d微積分同algebra 全部用wolfram alpha做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁同畀錢請槍有乜分別?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分別在wolfram alpha唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎, regular version free架喎, 係pro version先要錢!<br />\nAnyway, 你咁L醒嘅, 咁當年你Maths(尤其Pure Maths)功課咪鑊鑊滿分?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學滿分有閪用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48c59c7db4b00bcdd38d0ba86a78b96acf4729f","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想當年中學d微積分同algebra 全部用wolfram alpha做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁同畀錢請槍有乜分別?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分別在wolfram alpha唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎, regular version free架喎, 係pro version先要錢!<br />\nAnyway, 你咁L醒嘅, 咁當年你Maths(尤其Pure Maths)功課咪鑊鑊滿分?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學滿分有閪用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年讀書, 求學就是求分數嘛! 點會冇閪用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd92e9edff94ab9359a9f144c2b36f8f1542ec14","tid":193411,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"以前中學雞無呢D, 係用計數機既program計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245a6bfeb69d05933f4b63a43e5b4e5c06237ffa","tid":193411,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"1f5cbab7cb2281a615c4ecb2c282c7cc8cd9acc7","tid":193411,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"大學數都係用alpha計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年仲係測試版，已經好過mathematica好多"},{"pid":"beed7dc08289b38eb1c401c43c34519100baa219","tid":193411,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d23d09ab67625b95781f8bee60a056d321be5fe","tid":193411,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"中學嗰陣有同學做pure math成日用octave計<br />\n最後考AL pure差啲收咗皮，得個C仔"},{"pid":"15f833764a44fce4894b236177c5995b95348c77","tid":193411,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3aa6c5edff8bec51943786b305120447364b446","tid":193411,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁早就用program計，你考試死得仲慘呀"},{"pid":"83aaf6618c6c470cba891c27db36ba3f11676906","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"無意中發現到一個幾updated又多math articles同recommended math books嘅blog,<br />\n對maths有性趣嘅連登bros/sises可以一看:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mathblog.com/table-of-contents/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmathblog.com%2Ftable-of-contents%2F&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1a588da3\" target=\"_blank\">https://mathblog.com/table-of-contents/</a>"},{"pid":"ec8e64d38830cd992d7aaa1d7bef0b5cba11e086","tid":193411,"uid":73464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"用過MATLAB既物理撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb459911782535b91988c29b638524209417af3","tid":193411,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用過MATLAB既物理撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMATLAB simulink"},{"pid":"ea71e0cbc1119412be89becd35c537292daf3f0b","tid":193411,"uid":73464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用過MATLAB既物理撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMATLAB simulink</blockquote><br />\n工程撚好多會用到，不過MATLAB solve symbolic equations就唔夠Mathematica好"},{"pid":"3a7e23a885b9f4b7bb1fa0f5cad3eb618d393e17","tid":193411,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"咁 R 算唔覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8c0e9e3ac02d4f29f7ebad2d412eb0a7d386cf","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用過MATLAB既物理撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMATLAB simulink</blockquote><br />\n工程撚好多會用到，不過MATLAB solve symbolic equations就唔夠Mathematica好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實MATLAB強項係乜嘢? 點解出名過Mathematica咁多?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b6c8c40873c23f7589e0b2ad3d3db3efcd0717","tid":193411,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用過MATLAB既物理撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMATLAB simulink</blockquote><br />\n工程撚好多會用到，不過MATLAB solve symbolic equations就唔夠Mathematica好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實MATLAB強項係乜嘢? 點解出名過Mathematica咁多?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnumerical(工程撚) -&gt; matlab<br />\nsymbolic(puer math撚) -&gt; mathematica <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW,mathematica 有free version咩"},{"pid":"752f4ed5fc1d7049b952ade74cc511cfef42f38a","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁 R 算唔覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nR唔係齋玩到Stats架咩? 咁偏點可能算係CAS?! <br />\n要列入CAS範圍, 我估至少要玩到Algebra同Calculus先有資格囉!"},{"pid":"4e7ce01e6d624fd8d45effe2dd4a118ff65a995a","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"奇怪, 頭先試下係Maxima輸入<ins>solve(sin(x)=cos(x));</ins>, 佢居然return番同一條式出嚟, 完全無solve到個x值係乜! 反觀用Wolfram Alpha就solve得好正常, <span style=\"color: red;\">Maxima係咪有bug?</span>!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMaxima:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/231715_8a0b9599f7b4639e20fcd60d98ad276b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F231715_8a0b9599f7b4639e20fcd60d98ad276b.jpg&h=3a808cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWolfram Alpha:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/231826_09faef570d52b82962a066324bf99a01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F231826_09faef570d52b82962a066324bf99a01.jpg&h=ca6dc7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW, <span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識係Mathics度打同一條式出嚟solve到條equation</span>(用Mathematica嘅syntax打會出error!!!!)? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMathics:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/231937_c1c43028d05336558279aa76b38844bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F231937_c1c43028d05336558279aa76b38844bd.jpg&h=e6a3e8cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aefeb71a1c6ed7aea153c2a72755e07fc613910","tid":193411,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用過MATLAB既物理撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMATLAB simulink</blockquote><br />\n工程撚好多會用到，不過MATLAB solve symbolic equations就唔夠Mathematica好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實MATLAB強項係乜嘢? 點解出名過Mathematica咁多?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnumerical(工程撚) -&gt; matlab<br />\nsymbolic(puer math撚) -&gt; mathematica <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW,mathematica 有free version咩</blockquote><br />\nRaspberry pi裝raspbian就有full version<br />\n亦有keep住update新版<br />\n不過以rpi嘅效能行mathematica真係得啖笑<br />\n當玩具畀細路仔學吓數/programming就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e6e61d0c4179b5d3dc88d84b217037ca95c71a","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"有冇高人得閒解決下我上面提嘅兩條小問題? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0145d6fb702acc58cb2bda63fbd9fe95c9d9e239","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"原來宜家好多中小學生係用<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>GeoGebra</strong></span>呢隻graphing calculator嚟計數,plot graphs同solve equations(including algebra, calculus, and statistics), 呢隻software仲有埋個CAS view, 好L好用, 仲就手過Wolfram Alpha, Maxima, Mathics, SymPy呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , e.g.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/131820_ae4726a88ebd326bd2d170afdf00c532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%