,"tid":193411,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"劉鳴"},{"pid":"429d36cb75affde30dbef373f63793863ae5f57e","tid":193411,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩用<br />\n帶到入試場？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時做功課唔駛自己計咁晒時間, 慳番啲時間可以去打機囉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講中學定大學？<br />\n<br />\n中學數計機已經夠用<br />\n大學就根本做功課定要用"},{"pid":"8958eb547602599f878db819dd57ea55c6de48fb","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩用<br />\n帶到入試場？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時做功課唔駛自己計咁晒時間, 慳番啲時間可以去打機囉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講中學定大學？<br />\n<br />\n中學數計機已經夠用<br />\n大學就根本做功課定要用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閣下做乜9打漏咁多字, 語無倫次咁?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687f05ab705325090fcb9523fa136de84478cd34","tid":193411,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩用<br />\n帶到入試場？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順便話埋你知, GeoGebra係可以直頭用嚟考試架, 問你服未?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGeoGebra Exam: <a href=\"https://www.geogebra.org/m/syWFZsxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geogebra.org%2Fm%2FsyWFZsxM&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ebaf4fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.geogebra.org/m/syWFZsxM</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>GeoGebra Exam allows your students to use GeoGebra during exams without being able to access the Internet or other software installed on the computer. Leaving the GeoGebra window in any way triggers an alert, which can easily be spotted by the teacher and is docume